data.description: LIVE WHERE YOU PLAY: Heart of recreation, gateway to the Rubicon. Horse property, with access to miles of riding trails out the gate. Dru Barner campground and trails. close.  2.5 acres, 2 barns & 3 sheds fully fenced with panel paddocks at lower barn. The sound of the Irrigation ditch running through property will lull you to sleep. Single story home was rebuilt in 2008 with an attached apartment. NOW VACANT RENT WAS$1200 a month. newly installed solar panels and 2 mini splits to make heating and cooling cost efficient. Large back deck for entertaining. Pear tree, black berries, chestnut trees. Waiting for that special buyer to bring it back to its full potential. Main home has open floor plan with vaulted ceiling. Lovely Kitchen with large island, pantry closet, Laundry rm with sink outside access. Master suite with walkin closet, master bath with more closet space and storage, tub/shower. second bed, with lg closet, 2nd bath in hall tub/shower. Den/office could be 3rd bedroom. In-law apt has private entrance or could be accessed in main house also. It has 3 floors, main floor-Living rm and kitchen, 2nd floor-bedroom and full bath, 3rd floor is loft for extra bed or whatever is needed. So many possibilities.   on site estate sale coming soon with antiques and collectables.
